# AgentAudit — Quick pointer

**Local flight recorder for governed agent tool-use.** BLACKBOX is the internal engine name.

- **Repo:** github.com/blitzcrieg1/agentic-os · branch `master`
- **Run:** `scripts\start-dev.bat` → orchestrator `:8000` + dashboard `:3000`
- **Tests:** `cd apps\orchestrator && pip install -e ".[dev]" && pytest -q`
- **Validate:** `docs/agentaudit-dogfood-checklist.md`
- **Tier B:** `docs/external-agent-audit.md` · global hooks via `core/audit/hook_bootstrap.py` · `scripts/agentaudit_ingest.py`

## File map (start here — do not re-explore)

| Task | Path |
|---|---|
| Tier B ingest | `scripts/agentaudit_ingest.py`, `api/routes/audit.py`, `core/audit/ingest.py` |
| Audit canonical | `core/audit/canonical.py`, `external.py`, `sinks.py` |
| Flight recorder UI | `apps/dashboard/components/flight-recorder-panel.tsx` |
| Tier A demo skill | `vault/.system/skill-definitions/audit_demo.yaml` |
| Governed execution | `core/execution/service.py` → `run_skill()` |
| MCP host + allowlists | `core/drivers/host.py`, `vault/.system/drivers.json.example` |
| Hook bootstrap | `core/audit/hook_bootstrap.py` |

## First boot

```powershell
copy vault\.system\drivers.json.example vault\.system\drivers.json
copy apps\orchestrator\.env.agentaudit-demo apps\orchestrator\.env
scripts\start-dev.bat
python scripts\agentaudit_ingest.py selftest
```

